"""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""
"   General
"""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""

" Search
set hlsearch
set ignorecase
set smartcase

" numbering
set number
set relativenumber

" Use the system pasteboard
set clipboard=unnamed

" Comment code easily
nmap gcc :xcmenucmd Comment Selection<CR>

" Insert a line below current line
nmap <space>ij o<ESC>k

" Insert a line above the current line
nmap <space>ik O<ESC>j


""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""
"   SpaceCODE
"
" I use Spacemacs, thus, spacebar is my leader.
" However, that also means that I have some ingrained commands in my hands.
" Here, I'll be trying to replicate some of them with an approximation
" of their behaviour within Xcode.
"""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""

" Window management
nmap <space>wv :xcmenucmd Editor<CR>
nmap <space>ws :xcmenucmd Change Editor Orientation<CR>
nmap <space>wd :xcmenucmd Close Editor<CR>
nmap <space>wm :xcmenucmd Close Other Editors<CR>
nmap <space>gs :xcmenucmd Show Code Review<CR>

" Window navigation
nmap <space>wh <C-w>h
nmap <space>wl <C-w>l
nmap <space>wj <C-w>j
nmap <space>wk <C-w>k

" File commands
nmap <space>fs :xcmenucmd Save<CR>

" Search commands
nmap <space>pt :xcmenucmd Reveal in Project Navigator<CR>
nmap <space>pf :xcmenucmd Open Quickly...<CR>
nmap <space>/ :xcmenucmd Open Quickly...<CR>
nmap <space>sap :xcmenucmd Find in Project...<CR>
nmap <space>* viw:xccmd findSelectedSymbolInWorkspace<CR>

" Jumping
nmap gd :xcmenucmd Jump to Definition<CR>
nmap gc :xcmenucmd Show Code Actions<CR>

" Running & Building
nmap <space>cr :xcmenucmd Run<CR>
nmap <space>cb :xcmenucmd Build<CR>

" Testing
nmap <space>ct :xcmenucmd Test<CR>
nmap <space>cta :xcmenucmd Test Again<CR>
nmap <space>cts :xcmenucmd Test Selected Items<CR>

" Cleaning
nmap <space>ctk :xcmenucmd Clean Test Results<CR>
nmap <space>ck :xcmenucmd Clean Build Folder<CR>

" Toggles
nmap <space>tb viw:xccmd toggleBreakpointAtCurrentLine<CR>
nmap <space>ta :xcmenucmd Authors<CR>
nmap <space>tc :xcmenucmd Code Coverage<CR>
nmap <space>tm :xcmenucmd Minimap<CR>
nmap <space>tn :xcmenucmd Show Navigator<CR>
nmap <space>ti :xcmenucmd Show Inspector<CR>
nmap <space>td :xcmenucmd Show Debug Area<CR>
nmap <space>tw :xcmenucmd Invisibles<CR>

" Quitting
nmap <space>qq :xcmenucmd Quit Xcode<CR>
